    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015690/extras/1daba281a408023f385a0193f5cf0de8.avif?t=1750446088\" width=634 height=180 /></span>Well hello there beautiful! The name's Miss Wolfy and I'll be guiding you throughout this adventure (＾ *)✿ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Super Cursor</strong> is a challenging precision platformer where you control your very own mouse cursor, who is brought to life and given his own personality! Move through the world as you dodge obstacles and enemies who are stopping you from reaching your beloved princess. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Be careful though, as <strong>anything</strong> you touch will kill you instantly, making you start all over again! (WOW FUN!)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015690/extras/73a09d82694b1a9706331f1ecb554551.poster.avif?t=1750446088\" width=600 height=120 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015690/extras/73a09d82694b1a9706331f1ecb554551.webm?t=1750446088\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3015690/extras/73a09d82694b1a9706331f1ecb554551.mp4?t=1750446088\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Don't you worry, as only the tip of your cursor will cause damage to you! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Absolutely no mistakes are allowed, can you make it to the end and free the princess and myself, or will we be together forever and ever? (ʘ‿ʘ)ﾉ✿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dodge obstacles, enemies, and projectiles thrown your way</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat difficult bosses that will enrage you!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtracks, characters, and world!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online Co-op because two heads are better than one, right?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring personality to your very own cursor!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel through time!?</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unique gameplay that extends beyond the game?</p></li></ul>",
